item.title: CV
item.dc:creator: olumide53
item.content:encoded:
Back to Intro  

Skills

  • Extensive knowledge of data migration and integration between systems
  • Designing and developing Power BI dashboards
  • Designing and developing FileMaker business applications
  • Ability to work with any RDBMS
  • Developing reports using Crystal Reports and SSRS
  • Excellent analytical and problem-solving skills
  • Solid investigative techniques e.g. workshops, interviews, observation, prototyping
  • Managing projects, stakeholders and business change
  • Excellent in business and technical requirements documentation
  • Experienced in Problem Management, Change Request Management, Release Management, Incident Management

Achievements

  • Managed the implementation of an automated payments processing system which enhanced the processing of remittance advices and cheques. We eliminated paper processing thereby increasing operational efficiency and the velocity of cash flow
  • Led the successful implementation of a new web-based practice management system from the old legacy system. The efficiency gains meant doctors saw more patients which led to a 20% increase in revenue for the company
  • Member of a team that successfully implemented an online portal system of electronic planning application submission and e-payments for planning applications. The system enabled customers to have 24hr access to the planning application system, leading to increased customer satisfaction with provision of council services, and to efficiency gains within the council
  • Migrated successfully large datasets from an Ingres database system to SQL Server 2000, and completely rewrote statistical reports using Crystal Report 9.
Professional Experience
